{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/typeorm/typeorm/issues/11528","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/typeorm/typeorm","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/typeorm/typeorm/issues/11528/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/typeorm/typeorm/issues/11528/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/typeorm/typeorm/issues/11528/events","html_url":"https://github.com/typeorm/typeorm/issues/11528","id":3147376573,"node_id":"I_kwDOAyVBJc67mSe9","number":11528,"title":"Relax redis peer dependency to allow redis@^5 (in peerOptionalDependencies)","user":{"login":"StefaniOSApps","id":29314643,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI5MzE0NjQz","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/29314643?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/StefaniOSApps","html_url":"https://github.com/StefaniOSApps","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/StefaniOSApps/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/StefaniOSApps/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/StefaniOSApps/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/StefaniOSApps/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/StefaniOSApps/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/StefaniOSApps/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/StefaniOSApps/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/StefaniOSApps/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/StefaniOSApps/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":1,"created_at":"2025-06-15T11:19:42Z","updated_at":"2025-08-01T15:30:42Z","closed_at":"2025-08-01T15:30:42Z","author_association":"NONE","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"## Problem\n\nThe current `peerOptionalDependencies` entry for `redis` in TypeORM v0.3.23 is:\n\n```json\n\"redis\": \"^3.1.1 || ^4.0.0\"\n````\n\nThis blocks installation with `redis@5.x` under strict npm resolution (e.g. npm v7+), even though Redis is only required when using TypeORM's cache feature.\n\n## Why this matters\n\nMany users rely on `redis@5.x` directly (e.g. for Streams, Pub/Sub, etc.) and don't use TypeORM's Redis integration at all. Still, installation fails unless using `--legacy-peer-deps`.\n\nThis restriction creates unnecessary friction for setups where TypeORM and Redis are both used â€” independently.\n\n## Suggested fix\n\nRelax the peerOptional range in `package.json`:\n\n```json\n\"redis\": \"^3.1.1 || ^4.0.0 || ^5.0.0\"\n```\n\nOr ideally:\n\n```json\n\"redis\": \"*\"\n```\n\n...since it's an optional peer and not a hard requirement.\n\n## Environment\n\n* typeorm: 0.3.23\n* redis: 5.5.6\n* node: 22.x\n* npm: 10.x","closed_by":{"login":"gioboa","id":35845425,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM1ODQ1NDI1","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/35845425?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/gioboa","html_url":"https://github.com/gioboa","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gioboa/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gioboa/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gioboa/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gioboa/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gioboa/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gioboa/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gioboa/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gioboa/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gioboa/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/typeorm/typeorm/issues/1152